INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','page',0,1,1,'und',0,'<h3><br class=\"Apple-interchange-newline\" />[[{\"type\":\"media\",\"view_mode\":\"media_large\",\"fid\":\"101\",\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"\",\"class\":\"media-image\",\"style\":\"border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; margin-left: 10px; margin-right: 10px; float: right; width: 200px; height: 302px; \",\"typeof\":\"foaf:Image\"}}]]Meet Tamara...&nbsp;</h3><p>My passion for health and fitness is a direct result of personal experience. &nbsp;I know what it feels like to feel lethargic and tired from a long day, barely finding my drive to tie my running shoes, pull my hair back and head outside for a run. &nbsp;Slowly I start to feel the fresh air, enjoy the beauty of the mountains, and feel my shoes reassuringly hitting the trail as I work my way up the hill. &nbsp;I always tell clients that no matter what your mindset is before you start your workout; the end result is always the same&hellip;. Accomplishment. &nbsp;</p><div style=\"background-color: transparent; \"><p style=\"font-size: 15px; background-color: transparent; \"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; \">I began my journey of making health/fitness my career and passion by earning my Bachelor of Science in Exercise and Sport Medicine with a minor in Business Administration from Vanguard University in Southern California. &nbsp;From there, I managed a corporate wellness center where I had the opportunity to personal train, teach, and invest in a diverse population. &nbsp;I then moved onto a private studio where I furthered</span></font>my experience and knowledge directly related to the body, nutrition, and personal training. &nbsp;It was during that time that I met my husband and my beautiful daughter soon followed. &nbsp;During this change in my life, I started my own personal training business where I have the ability to fully engage one-on-one with my clients. &nbsp;I absolutely love my job because I get to see people&rsquo;s lives change right before my eyes. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><h3 style=\"background-color: transparent; \">[[{\"type\":\"media\",\"view_mode\":\"media_preview\",\"fid\":\"131\",\"attributes\":{\"alt\":\"\",\"class\":\"media-image\",\"style\":\"border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; margin-left: 5px; margin-right: 5px; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; float: left; \",\"typeof\":\"foaf:Image\"}}]]<font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; \">My mission&hellip;</span></font></h3><p style=\"font-size: 15px; background-color: transparent; \"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; \">My goal for my clients is simple: help them reach their physical potential through exercise and proper nutrition. &nbsp;The irony is that the simple goal translates into ALL facets of the client&rsquo;s life. &nbsp;Once clients personally feel the many benefits of improving their health through exercise and sound nutrition, empowerment begins to transpire. Clients are now doing exercises they never dreamed of doing. &nbsp;They&rsquo;re feeling energetic, and actually wanting to eat healthy. They begin to see noticeable difference in their body and get off medications. &nbsp;Then the ultimate happens- the changes and hard work it takes to reach these goals turns into a lifestyle. &nbsp;That lifestyle now created is life changing. &nbsp;I see it every day, and that is why this job is so rewarding.</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; \"> &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font></p></div><h3 style=\"font-size: 15px; background-color: transparent; \"><font class=\"Apple-style-span\" color=\"#000000\" face=\"\'Times New Roman\'\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></font></h3><p style=\"background-color: transparent; \"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: \'Times New Roman\'; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap; \">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>','','full_html');
INSERT INTO `field_data_body` VALUES ('node','blog',0,6,6,'und',0,'<p>A blog post is a way to communicate your thoughts and ideas with associated images or videos. It is also a great way to engage your site visitors by allowing comments on your posts. Note that besides personal blogs, a single Drupal Gardens site can also host multiple blogs, each authored by a different user, which is a great way to give organizations a voice.</p><p>To add another Blog post, click Add content > Blog post.</p><p><a href=\"http://www.drupalgardens.com/learnmore/blog\" target=\"_blank\">Learn more</a></p>','','safe_html');
