INSERT INTO `search_dataset` VALUES (1,'node',' about meet tamara  my passion for health and fitness is a direct result of personal experience i know what it feels like to feel lethargic and tired from a long day barely finding my drive to tie my running shoes pull my hair back and head outside for a run slowly i start to feel the fresh air enjoy the beauty of the mountains and feel my shoes reassuringly hitting the trail as i work my way up the hill i always tell clients that no matter what your mindset is before you start your workout the end result is always the same accomplishment i began my journey of making health fitness my career and passion by earning my bachelor of science in exercise and sport medicine with a minor in business administration from vanguard university in southern california from there i managed a corporate wellness center where i had the opportunity to personal train teach and invest in a diverse population i then moved onto a private studio where i furthered my experience and knowledge directly related to the body nutrition and personal training it was during that time that i met my husband and my beautiful daughter soon followed during this change in my life i started my own personal training business where i have the ability to fully engage oneonone with my clients i absolutely love my job because i get to see people s lives change right before my eyes  my mission  my goal for my clients is simple help them reach their physical potential through exercise and proper nutrition the irony is that the simple goal translates into all facets of the client s life once clients personally feel the many benefits of improving their health through exercise and sound nutrition empowerment begins to transpire clients are now doing exercises they never dreamed of doing they re feeling energetic and actually wanting to eat healthy they begin to see noticeable difference in their body and get off medications then the ultimate happens the changes and hard work it takes to reach these goals turns into a lifestyle that lifestyle now created is life changing i see it every day and that is why this job is so rewarding      ',0);
