INSERT INTO `search_dataset` VALUES (81,'node',' personal training personal training inhome inhome training is a great way to eliminate the obstacles if you find that you are pressed for time like the comfort of your home or just want the convenience of a trainer coming to you then this is a great option i provide all necessary equipment for a stellar workout in your own home inhome training can be done as individual sessions or partner group partner group training this option is ideal for those that like the accountability support or competition of a friend or family member i find that the majority of clients that do partner or group sessions are more consistent with their workouts and healthy habits outside of the time we have together than those that do individual sessions there is something to be said for additional accountability another perk of this option is the discounted rate it offers individual training oneonone focused training it s me you and a world of possibilities for a successful motivated workout this option is perfect for those that need and thrive off of the oneonone focus i provide in the training sessions all personal training sessions include the following  free initial consultation   this is where we meet and i explore your goals expectations and get to know your individual needs and wants  baseline measurements  in order to have a tangible assessment of your progress throughout our training baseline measurements are needed included are the following bia body fat testing girth measurements blood pressure heart rate weight and physical testing all testing methods are within accordance of acsm nutrition consultation  nutrition is a key component in reaching anyone s fitness health goals i am a strong proponent of the necessity to combine exercise with proper nutrition and i will ensure my clients are knowledgeable to what that entails we will explore any changes that need to be made and the necessary accountability that is needed to aid my clients to making smart choices i am available at all times via phone email or text if a client has questions regarding a food choice etc many clients find it helpful to text me at a work luncheon to ask what to order at a particular restaurant you have me at your disposal  measurement reassessment  after a few weeks of training we will take measurements again to have tangible objective results from our time together  workout designs outside of our time together  ever wonder how you re supposed to reach your goals if you are only meeting with your trainer twice a week i ensure that my clients have workouts to do outside of our time that are specifically designed to that individual s goals and available equipment i also help the client stay accountable his her workouts outside of our time together  ',0);
